    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 small scratches here and there, but no dents or rust. The interior is clean and functional with typical signs of use.",
